    public class AutoTagForSavepointCommitterOperator<CommitT,GlobalCommitT>
extends Object
implements org.apache.flink.streaming.api.operators.OneInputStreamOperator<CommitT,CommitT>, org.apache.flink.streaming.api.operators.SetupableStreamOperator, org.apache.flink.streaming.api.operators.BoundedOneInput
    Commit Committable for each snapshot using the CommitterOperator. At the same time, tags are automatically created for each flink savepoint.
